]div
[h4 id=Otherstreamingmediasites
 
	" Other streaming media sites
	$LF
]h4
[ul 
	[li 
		"Publishers are welcome to upload publications to other streaming media sites such as 
		[a class=extlink href=http://www.nicovideo.jp/ rel=nofollow 
			"Nicovideo
		]a
		". It is preferred, however, that one of the above sites be used - the site is currently configured to only accept streaming links from a handful of streaming sites.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"Links to these sites should only be on the movie page if they link to official (properly subtitled and described) encodes.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
